Sony has announced that PlayStation Plus members who subscribe to Spotify Premium through the PlayStation Store will receive 10% off their subscription fees. The promotion is valid for all PlayStation 4 owners and will last until 10 October 2018. The savings will be applied to monthly recurring Spotify Premium fees for as long as players continue to maintain an active PlayStation Plus membership. PS4 PlayStation Plus members who subscribe to Spotify Premium through PlayStation Store will automatically receive the 10% savings. PS4 owners can also link their existing Spotify account to their account on the PlayStation Network to access their playlists.